# Doris
# =====
IMAPStore doris-remote
    Host imap01.binero.se
    User sebastian@doris.tech
    PassCmd "pass Doris/loopia/sebastian@doris.tech"
    SSLType IMAPS
    SSLVersions TLSv1.2
    AuthMechs LOGIN
    PipeLineDepth 3 # nr of concurrent cmds

MaildirStore doris-local
    SubFolders Verbatim
    Path ~/Mail/doris/
    Inbox ~/Mail/doris/INBOX
    MaxSize 400k

Channel doris-inbox
    Master :doris-remote:
    Slave :doris-local:
    CopyArrivalDate Yes
    Create Both
    Expunge Both
    SyncState *
    Patterns "INBOX" "Sent Messages" "Archive" "Deleted Messages"

